  "texts": [
    "3 Approach using rules Cai et al. (2021b) first described the evaluation of the ACOSQE task, which created four baseline methods: Double-Propagation-ACOS, JET-ACOS, TAS-BERT-ACOS, and Extract-Classify-ACOS.",
    "These systems were adapted from existing AOPE, ACSTE, or AOSTE approaches to be compatible with the ACOSQE task.",
    "Following their research, a new series of works have been proposed in this field.",
    "Table 8 shows a comparison of methods in Rule-based, BERT-based, Bart-based, and T5-based benchmark for the ACOSQE task based on ACOS-Dataset.",
    "This section will cover the pipeline method with rule-based (Double-Propagation-ACOS) on the ACOS-Dataset (Cai et al. 2021b)."
  ]
}